translation.Name: Buak_Note_18
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Today, I closed the deal! Location I picked out won’t have a window like I was hoping, but that is the art of the deal. We’ll have plenty of space, labs and if anything goes wrong, we’ll be able to contain anything that goes wrong which was one of the big factors in my decision. We’ll keep the company’s image nice and clean. Oh, and you can’t smell that smell the other locations had.
